U.K. Stocks Decline; Antofagasta Leads Slide in Benchmark FTSE 100 Index

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-05-03T10:52:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-03/u-k-stocks-decline-antofagasta-leads-slide-in-benchmark-ftse-100-index.html
U.K. stocks declined, with the
benchmark FTSE 100 Index falling 15.64, or 0.2 percent, to
6,054.26 at 11:50 a.m. in  London . Antofagasta fell 3.2 percent
to 1,323 pence, leading losses on the FTSE 100.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
